    {
      "id": "8074db4b-4f8b-4002-8121-d1f17285542a",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$$I:(a,b,c) \\Leftrightarrow \\left\\{\\begin{array}{ccc} 6-a-b-c     &=& r\\sqrt3    \\cr\n                                    4a-2b+c-3   &=& r\\sqrt{21} \\cr\n                                    a+4b-2c-3   &=& r\\sqrt{21} \\cr\n                                    12-7a-b+5c  &=& r\\sqrt{75} \\cr \\end{array}\\right.\n              \\Leftrightarrow \\left\\{\\begin{array}{ccc} 2a &=& 9 - 2\\sqrt 7\\cr\n                          2b &=& 6 - \\sqrt7  \\cr\n                          2c &=& 3           \\cr\n                          2r &=& \\sqrt{21}-2\\sqrt3.\\cr \\end{array}\\right.$$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math display\">\\[I:(a,b,c) \\Leftrightarrow \\left\\{\\begin{array}{ccc} 6-a-b-c     &amp;=&amp; r\\sqrt3    \\cr\n                                    4a-2b+c-3   &amp;=&amp; r\\sqrt{21} \\cr\n                                    a+4b-2c-3   &amp;=&amp; r\\sqrt{21} \\cr\n                                    12-7a-b+5c  &amp;=&amp; r\\sqrt{75} \\cr \\end{array}\\right.\n              \\Leftrightarrow \\left\\{\\begin{array}{ccc} 2a &amp;=&amp; 9 - 2\\sqrt 7\\cr\n                          2b &amp;=&amp; 6 - \\sqrt7  \\cr\n                          2c &amp;=&amp; 3           \\cr\n                          2r &amp;=&amp; \\sqrt{21}-2\\sqrt3.\\cr \\end{array}\\right.\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
